{"tid":910074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醒醒吧！他10歲就娶老婆　8歲蘿莉成人妻","createTime":"2018-11-21T01:35:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T05:40:17.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"14f8731703acbd1c756e37f17c0c9a04543181da","tid":910074,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T01:35:31.000Z","msg":"羅馬尼亞近日流出一段婚禮影片，引發爭議，因為片中的新郎新娘年齡，分別年僅10歲與8歲。<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，相信拍攝地點是多爾日縣(Dolj)，當地的吉普賽人正在舉辦一場傳統婚禮，但新郎年僅10歲，新娘也不過是個8歲的女童。影片拍下主持人開心地唱著傳統歌曲，眾親友們也開心慶祝，而女童出嫁，則穿上粉紅色的嫁衣，並仿效成人濃妝豔抹，禮服還故意做出巨乳的樣子。<br />\n報導指出，相信這是一場吉普賽人的傳統婚禮，當地聚落仍留有早婚的習慣，而女童嫁到夫家後，並不會馬上行房，還能繼續和自己的原生家庭住在一起，數年後再成為正式夫妻。這樣的童婚，比較像是訂婚的概念。就有網友沃清(Don Vochin)指出，這場婚禮並非正式婚禮，男童與女童必須等在長大之後，再進行正式婚禮。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181121/640_5d1a430d00e92f5c8eca141738e43aaf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181121%2F640_5d1a430d00e92f5c8eca141738e43aaf.jpg&h=65763eef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181121/1470244/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181121%2F1470244%2F&d=urbJlywAQcMBFL9ikkylngHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=d806a3c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181121%2F1470244%2F&h=f13b7efc\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181121/1470244/</a>"},{"pid":"6529cdea93849c194801d6d60ebd20dfb0d8a86a","tid":910074,"uid":215111,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T01:38:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd8e88b2cd23ff4a76be01a84494e0ebad8240b","tid":910074,"uid":294,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T01:40:27.000Z","msg":"<i